### TTRPG Systems

### Description
This repository contains core resolution systems adapted from a custom TTRPG ruleset
It includes modular mechanics designed to be reused in larger projects


### Features
- Skill check system using formula
	score = skill -3d6 + modifier
- critical success and failure mechanics based on skill thresholds

### Status
This is not a playable game
Skill checks - Completed

### Future features
- default stats applicable for all characters (STR, DEX, CON, WL, IQ)
- Expanded combat mechanics
- Integration into a full game

